title: Dr. Brown's® Formula Mixing Pitcher
description:
Dr. Brown's Formula Mixing Pitcher dissolves formula quickly with no clumping. Helps limit the amount of air in the formula.

• Mixes formula quickly without clumping
• Prepare up to four 8 oz/250 ml bottles at once
• Helps minimize air in the formula
• Spill-free locking lid / No-drip spout
• 32 oz/960 ml pitcher / Soft-grip handle
• Easy to use / Dishwasher safe
